    An implementation of interface CharStream, where the stream is assumed to contain only ASCII characters (with java-like unicode escape processing).
    SubParserFactory
    Factory for creating a SubParser sharing configuration, state, and prefixes, but with an independent input stream, to be used, e.g., for parsing arguments in data source declarations.
